类 LongSeatSetting

  • com.veepoo.protocol.model.settings.LongSeatSetting

  • public class LongSeatSetting

    Created by timaimee on 2017/2/13.

    • 构造器详细资料

      • LongSeatSetting

        public LongSeatSetting(int startHour,
                       int startMiute,
                       int endHour,
                       int endMinute,
                       int threshold,
                       boolean isOpen)

        结束时间要大于开始时间，阈值要小于两个时间的差值

        参数:
        startHour - 开始的小时
        startMiute - 开始的分钟
        endHour - 结束的小时
        endMinute - 结束的分钟
        threshold - 阈值：多久没动过，手表就会提醒
        isOpen - 是否打开
